The United Bank for Africa (UBA) has rewarded another set of 100 loyal customers with a total of N10 million in the UBA Bumper Account Draw. The 100 customers won N100,000 each in this month’s edition of the draw which began in January 2020. The virtual draw which was held at the UBA Head Office in Lagos was transmitted live via the Facebook platform in strict compliance with social distancing rules as directed by the Federal and Lagos State governments. UBA’s Group Head, Consumer and Retail Banking, Jude Anele, who congratulated the lucky winners, said they were rewarded for their loyalty to the bank. Dear valued readers, subscribe to the Daily Trust e-paper to continue enjoying our diet of authoritative news. Kindly subscribe here UBA rewards 100 'Bumper Account’ customers with N10m UBA customers win N30m in Wise Savers promo UBA unveils UBA Gunners Promo